<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Detective_fiction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Detective debuts and swansongs">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Detective debuts and swansongs</span></h2>
